CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

March 3, 2008

[Cite as 03/0312008 Case Announcements, 2008-Ohio-822.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2007-2150. Walburn v. Dunlap.

Vinton App. No. 06CA655, 2007-Ohio-5398. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Vinton County. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion to supplement record,

It is ordered by the court that the motion is granted. The clerk of the court of appeals shall transmit to the Clerk of this court the record in Vinton County Court of Appeals Case No. 06CA653.
